			</div>
			<br />



			<strong>
				<a href="http://www.cdc.gov/mmwr/preview/mmwrhtml/mm6313a4.htm" class = "link">
					Notes from the Field: Calls to Poison Centers for Exposures to Electronic Cigarettes—United States, September 2010–February 2014.
				</a>
				<p>
					Kevin Chatham-Stephens, Royal Law, Ethel Taylor, Paul Melstrom, Rebecca Bunnell, Baoguang Wang, Benjamin Apelberg, Joshua G. Schier
				</p>
			</strong>
			<p>
				This oft-cited study indicates a significant rise in the calls to poison control centers for nicotine exposure. The concentrated nicotine in the juice can be dangerous if not handled properly. Never drink the liquid and keep it away from children.
			</p>
			<%= render "science_citation", id: "notes-from-the-field" %>
