			<strong>
			<a href="" class= "link">
					Variable and potentially fatal amounts of nicotine in e-cigarette nicotine solutions.
				</a>
				<p>
				Jennifer M. Cameron, Donelle N. Howell, John R. White, David M. Andrenyak, Matthew E. Layton, John M. Roll
				</p>
			</strong>
			<p>
				This is a great brochure-length discussion of nicotine toxicity. IMPORTANT: The fatal dose of nicotine in adults is 30 - 60 milligrams in adults and 10 milligrams in children. So if you vape 30mg/ml juice your 5ml dropper bottle contains150 mg of nicotine, well over the fatal dose. Be careful and keep your supplies out of reach of children.
			</p>
